Init-Containers

Sidecar(init container that always runs)

Approaches for scaling:
1. Scaling Cluster infra(we don't do vertical scaling usually)
a. manual- using kubeadm join <new node>
b. automated- using autoscaler

2. Scaling workloads
a. HPA (Horizontal Pod Autoscaler)- 
kubectl autoscale deployment my-app --cpu-percent=50 --min=1 --max=10
kubectl get hpa
b. VPA (Vertical Pod Autoscaler)
